title: Cuno new Chancellor
subtitle: Ebert calls the former DVP member, now independent, buisnessman Wilhelm Cuno to be Chancellor. 
view-if: year == 1922 and month == 11 and wirth_2_failed == 1
max-visits: 1 
tags: event 
new-page: true 
on-arrival: chancellor = 'Cuno'; chancellor_party = 'I'; in_weimar_coalition = 0
face-image: img/portraits/CunoWilhelm.jpg 
  
= Cuno to be Chancellor

Ebert calls the former DVP member, now independent, buisnessman Wilhelm Cuno to be Chancellor.

He offers the SPD to join his government of experienced buisnessmen and pragmatic politicians in a broad coalition.

- @join_cuno: The SPD joins the Cuno government.
- @tolerate_cuno: The SPD tolerates Cuno and his bourgeois cabinet.
- @oppose_cuno: The SPD will not work with this government despite the wish of the President.
  
@join_cuno
on-arrival: spd_in_government = 1; dvp_in_government = 1; z_in_government = 1; ddp_in_government = 1; in_grand_coalition = 1; leverage = 25; foreign_minister = 'Rosenberg'; foreign_minister_party = 'I'; interior_minister = 'Oeser'; interior_minister_party = 'DDP'; justice_minister = 'Heinze'; justice_minister_party = 'DVP'; labor_minister = 'Brauns'; labor_minister_party = 'Z'; reichswehr_minister = 'Geßler'; reichswehr_minister_party = 'DDP'; economic_minister = 'Becker'; economic_minister_party = 'DVP'; finance_minister = 'Hermes'; finance_minister_party = 'Z'; agriculture_minister = 'Luther'; agriculture_minister_party = 'I'; transport_minister = 'Groener'; transport_minister_party = 'I'; postal_miniter = 'Stingl'; postal_minister_party = 'BVP'; workers_spd -= 2
choose-if: left_strength <= 20 and reformist_strength >= 50 and early_dvp_cooperation >= 2

The SPD agress to join the Cuno government.

- @selection_of_ministries

@selection_of_ministries
title: Select our ministries

We can choose a few ministries. Controlling a ministry allows us to directly effect policy in that area.

- @labor
- @interior_main
- @finance
- @economic
- @justice
- @foreign
- @agriculture
- @reichswehr
- @transport
- @done_cuno
  
@labor
title: Labor Ministry
subtitle: Taking the Labor Ministry is expected of us.
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
tags: mins_1928
choose-if: leverage >= 5
view-if: labor_minister_party != "SPD"
on-arrival: leverage -= 5; labor_minister_party = "SPD"; labor_minister = "Wissell"
go-to: selection_of_ministries

Rudolf Wissell of the <span style="color: #c00000;">**SPD**</span> has been appointed labor minister.

@interior_main
title: Interior Ministry
subtitle: Taking the Interior Ministry is expected of us. The Interior Ministry controls domestic security.
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
choose-if: leverage >= 5
view-if: interior_minister_party != "SPD"
tags: mins_1928

- @appoint_severing
- @appoint_sollmann
- @cancel_interior

@appoint_severing
title: Carl Severing
subtitle: (reformist).
choose-if: leverage >= 5
unavailable-subtitle: We do not have enough leverage.
